{
  "texts": [
    "A comprehensive list of the remaining 12 SAAs is provided in the Appendix.",
    "Inputters were blinded to the outcome (i.e.",
    "the correct solution) and recoded the triage levels as provided by the SAAs.",
    "These results were then reviewed by the lead author (MK).",
    "In instances where the inputters came up with different results, we considered a vignette correctly solved if at least one of them had recorded the correct solution."
  ]
}